snippet.title: Norman's Night In - 2017 Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW!

App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/normans-night-in/id1437084898?ls=1
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1034870/Normans_Night_In/

Norman's Night In is a mobile Metroidvania platformer that tells the tale of Norman and his fateful fall into the world of cave.

Use slingshot controls to solve puzzles, face unfamiliar cave beasties, and explore the unseen world by the light of your new bowling ball.

More at: https://www.bactriangames.com/
